1.0.name: wordpress/multi-video-box
1.0.description: This plug-in allows you to display groups of videos in a single box. It uses an AJAX-driven tab system to load selected videos. The plug-in currently supports the use of videos hosted on YouTube, Vimeo, Daily Motion, Vevo, Metacafe, MuchShare, NowVideo, VideoMega, ShareVid, Flashx.TV, and Putlocker. CSS is fully-customizable.
